data.description: Fully renovated single story home on a .59 acre lot in Crest with spectacular mountain and valley views. Brand new kitchen with all new appliances. Newer white dual pane windows throughout the entire home and skylights.  Three large bedrooms plus an office area and an enclosed area that has been used as a workshop.  Large yard in front and back with views on both sides and three storage sheds. Ample space with lots of possibilities and plenty of room to be creative. This one is extremely private and quiet which makes it a gem!!!
